512851080902708e-07, \"text\": \"Monika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monika_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monika_Mann\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"a good night's rest\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Indian Olympic Association is planning to provide them with sleeping pods.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sleeping pods\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep is apparently an Olympic-sized problem these days.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-sized problem\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Javelin thrower Neeraj Chopra spent many nights tossing and turning before his gold-medal event at the Tokyo games in 2021.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999950277925, \"rank\": 4.859642220948003e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many nights\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"his gold-medal event\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shooter Abhinav Bindra did not sleep at all the night before his big day in Rio.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abhinav Bindra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999997176092109, \"rank\": 2.823910992433203e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his big day\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Sharma tells theIndian Express\\\"ignorance about sleep is quite profound\\\" among athletes.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dr Sharma\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"theIndian Express\\\"ignorance\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though both Bindra and Chopra won golds, in an intensely competitive forum where everyone is looking for an edge, \\\"getting optimum sleep and restorative sleep definitely gives them that edge.\\\"\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bindra\", \"score\": 0.9011311734315588, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bindra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bindra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"an intensely competitive forum\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"an edge\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"optimum sleep\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"restorative sleep\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"that edge\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharma is couching this in terms of removing the chance that lack of sleep might cost India a medal.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999244593457473, \"rank\": 7.55463532923954e-05, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sharma\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also read:The age of the influencer is truly upon usBut even those of us not chasing an Olympic medal know a thing or two about poor sleep.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The age\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the influencer\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"usBut\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"even those\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"poor sleep\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was the kind of boy who fell asleep as soon as his head hit the pillow.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"boy\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the pillow\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I am the man who often wakes up with a jolt in the middle of night and frets and fumes listening to the city asleep around him.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"a jolt\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"frets\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"fumes\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night I go to bed wondering what kind of night it will be.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night of restful sleep feels like a minor victory.I understand it is part of growing older.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every night\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"restful sleep\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"a minor victory\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is something deeper going on.The Sleep Survey 2024conducted by ResMed, a medical device company, surveyed 17 countries.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"The Sleep Survey\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"ResMed\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical device company\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"17 countries\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It concluded that only 27% of Indians reported a good night's sleep each week.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9973778045242311, \"rank\": 0.0016645993583474217, \"text\": \"Indians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 27%\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"a good night's sleep\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 2019 study by fitness band maker Fitbit concluded after analysing the data from Fitbit users that Indians were the second most sleep-deprived, among all the countries they surveyed, with Japan heading the list.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fitbit\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\"}, {\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fitbit\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\"}, {\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9973778045242311, \"rank\": 0.0016645993583474217, \"text\": \"Indians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9803891662861449, \"rank\": 0.019476335703717804, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A 2019 study\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"all the countries\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And their REM (rapid eye movement) sleep time was among the lowest in the world.I know this only too well.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(rapid eye movement\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Worried about my sleep, I got one of the fitness bands that would help monitor it.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sleep\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"the fitness bands\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It ended up adding to my stress.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my stress\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt like I was taking a sleeping test every night.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sleeping test\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if I woke up refreshed and happy, it was never good enough for the nitpicking fitness band.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nitpicking fitness band\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Try going to bed earlier,\\\" it would scold me.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My deep sleep time was invariably too low.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My deep sleep time\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not strain yourself too much, keep good mood, make reasonable arrangements for work and rest time, and do more exercise to keep fit,\\\" it chirpily advised me.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good mood\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"reasonable arrangements\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"rest time\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"more exercise\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to smack it.The first time sleeplessness really hit me, I was recovering from jet lag.\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first time sleeplessness\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"jet lag\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night, no matter what time I went to bed, I would bolt awake somewhere between 2 and 3 in the morning.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what time\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At some point I thought some mechanism had just broken inside me and I would never get my sleep back.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"some mechanism\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"my sleep\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going to sleep without worrying about it felt like the ultimate luxury.Now my social media shows me endless ads for pillows, sleep yoga sessions, chewable melatonin tablets and herbal supplements.\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ultimate luxury\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"my social media\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"endless ads\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"pillows\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep yoga sessions\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"chewable melatonin tablets\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"herbal supplements\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had no idea there was an entire cottage industry around getting to sleep and staying asleep.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"an entire cottage industry\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I started measuring my caffeine intake with a tooth comb, watched endless videos of the 4-7-8 breathing relaxation exercise, carefully rearranged my bed for optimal sleeping comfort and tried to give myself a cut-off time with digital devices.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my caffeine intake\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"a tooth comb\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"endless videos\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4-7-8 breathing relaxation exercise\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"my bed\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal sleeping comfort\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"a cut-off time\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"digital devices\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But sleep proved to be an elusive creature, sneakingly evading all the traps and temptations I had laid out for it.When I was a child, no one really read me bedtime stores.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3492}, {\"ngram\": \"an elusive creature\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"all the traps\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3559}, {\"ngram\": \"temptations\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3616}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"bedtime stores\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My parents would turn off the main light and turn on a bedside lamp.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My parents\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"the main light\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"a bedside lamp\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father would sit and read the paper by the light of the lamp, half-listening to my mother as she filled him in about the day in a low voice.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My father\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3734}, {\"ngram\": \"the paper\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3776}, {\"ngram\": \"the lamp\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"about the day\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3852}, {\"ngram\": \"a low voice\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would lie in bed looking at the strange deformed shadows the bedside lamp cast on the ceiling.\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3887}, {\"ngram\": \"the strange deformed shadows\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3927}, {\"ngram\": \"the bedside lamp\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceiling\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My favourite sleep ritual was to pull the covers over me, hug my bolster pillow orpaash-baalish, and make up little stories in my head.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My favourite sleep\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3984}, {\"ngram\": \"the covers\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"little stories\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4089}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would imagine that under thatpaash-baalishwas a secret world where my toys and I could have a picnic.\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thatpaash\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4138}, {\"ngram\": \"a secret world\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"my toys\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4178}, {\"ngram\": \"a picnic\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was something Enid Blyton-ish about the whole affair but it worked like a charm.\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4226, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7176772293675345e-38, \"text\": \"Enid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4225}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole affair\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"a charm\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would be asleep long before I managed to come up with a full menu for the picnic.\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full menu\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4360}, {\"ngram\": \"the picnic\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Years later someone told me that the biggest sleep-aid I had back then was not my imaginary picnics, but a sense of security about the real world around me.\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4396}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sleep-aid\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4431}, {\"ngram\": \"my imaginary picnics\", \"from\": 4456, \"to\": 4476}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4501}, {\"ngram\": \"the real world\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was comfort in hearing the low voices of my parents, in knowing that I would wake up to them the next day.\", \"from\": 4534, \"to\": 4646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4551}, {\"ngram\": \"the low voices\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4577}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 4581, \"to\": 4591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The murmur of their voices was the white noise lulling me to sleep.As adults we struggle to find that security in a world which seems increasingly on edge.\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The murmur\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4657}, {\"ngram\": \"their voices\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"the white noise\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4693}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"that security\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4768}, {\"ngram\": \"edge\", \"from\": 4797, \"to\": 4801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Work, relationships and our own health all feel increasingly insecure.\", \"from\": 4803, \"to\": 4873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Work\", \"from\": 4803, \"to\": 4807}, {\"ngram\": \"relationships\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"our own health\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep is but a natural casualty.\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4879}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural casualty\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A ruffled mind is a ruffled pillow,\\\" the author Charlotte Bronte is reputed to have said.\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4956, \"end\": 4972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\", \"score\": 0.9999999619840317, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Bronte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A ruffled mind\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4922}, {\"ngram\": \"a ruffled pillow\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We live in very ruffled times indeed.When I would wake up with a start in the dead of night at first it would make me anxious.\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very ruffled times\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5027}, {\"ngram\": \"a start\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"the dead\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I try to make peace with it.\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I stand on the balcony looking at the empty street in an entirely different light, the streetlights almost forlorn and ghostly.\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the empty street\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"an entirely different light\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recognise the street dogs out on patrol.\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5318}, {\"ngram\": \"patrol\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rats come out of holes and scurry around looking for food.\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rats\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"holes\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5365}, {\"ngram\": \"scurry\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5376}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A sudden noise somewhere sets off a cawing frenzy among unseen crows.\", \"from\": 5402, \"to\": 5471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cawing frenzy\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5451}, {\"ngram\": \"unseen crows\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I see the vegetable vendor doggedly pushing a cart of cabbages and tomatoes to set up for the next day.\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vegetable vendor\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5498}, {\"ngram\": \"a cart\", \"from\": 5516, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"cabbages\", \"from\": 5526, \"to\": 5534}, {\"ngram\": \"tomatoes\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5547}, {\"ngram\": \"the next day\", \"from\": 5562, \"to\": 5574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes a drunk staggers down the street jabbing at his phone probably trying to book an Uber.\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drunk staggers\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5602}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5618}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5639}, {\"ngram\": \"an Uber\", \"from\": 5664, \"to\": 5671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young men who work at the cheap restaurant across the street wash dishes late into the night and finally relax, sprawled around the front steps, immersed in the flickering light of videos on their phones.\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The young men\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5686}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheap restaurant\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5719}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 5727, \"to\": 5737}, {\"ngram\": \"dishes\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5749}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5769}, {\"ngram\": \"the front steps\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5820}, {\"ngram\": \"the flickering light\", \"from\": 5834, \"to\": 5854}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 5858, \"to\": 5864}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 5868, \"to\": 5880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a rhythm here too, a soundscape that rustles to life once all the shops are shut and the buses and trams fall silent.When I think back to childhood stories, the problem seems to have always been too much sleep as opposed to too little.\", \"from\": 5882, \"to\": 6126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rhythm\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5899}, {\"ngram\": \"a soundscape\", \"from\": 5910, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5939, \"to\": 5943}, {\"ngram\": \"all the shops\", \"from\": 5949, \"to\": 5962}, {\"ngram\": \"the buses\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 5985}, {\"ngram\": \"trams\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 5995}, {\"ngram\": \"childhood stories\", \"from\": 6029, \"to\": 6046}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 6048, \"to\": 6059}, {\"ngram\": \"too much sleep\", \"from\": 6086, \"to\": 6100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kumbhakarna, Rip van Winkle and Sleeping Beauty all had sleep disorders but none of them were afflicted by insomnia.\", \"from\": 6127, \"to\": 6243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6127, \"end\": 6138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\", \"score\": 0.9999999998181011, \"rank\": 1.8200280897676406e-10, \"text\": \"Kumbhakarna\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\"}, {\"begin\": 6140, \"end\": 6154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4143465589471975e-57, \"text\": \"Rip van Winkle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleeping Beauty\", \"from\": 6159, \"to\": 6174}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep disorders\", \"from\": 6183, \"to\": 6198}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6207}, {\"ngram\": \"insomnia\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the Bengali fairytales I read had princesses who kept falling asleep and needed some prince with a golden wand to wake them.\", \"from\": 6244, \"to\": 6373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6253, \"end\": 6260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\", \"score\": 0.9999605449064164, \"rank\": 3.945664875035729e-05, \"text\": \"Bengali\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"princesses\", \"from\": 6283, \"to\": 6293}, {\"ngram\": \"some prince\", \"from\": 6329, \"to\": 6340}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden wand\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Too much sleep was scary in those fairytales.\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Too much sleep\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6388}, {\"ngram\": \"those fairytales\", \"from\": 6402, \"to\": 6418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rip van Winkle woke up after 20 years to find that his wife was long dead and the American revolution had happened.\", \"from\": 6420, \"to\": 6535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6420, \"end\": 6434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4143465589471975e-57, \"text\": \"Rip van Winkle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\"}, {\"begin\": 6502, \"end\": 6521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\", \"score\": 0.9999290548022813, \"rank\": 7.095023122573333e-05, \"text\": \"American revolution\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 6449, \"to\": 6457}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 6471, \"to\": 6479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleeping Beauty pricked her finger on a spinning wheel and did not wake up for a century.\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleeping Beauty\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6551}, {\"ngram\": \"her finger\", \"from\": 6560, \"to\": 6570}, {\"ngram\": \"a spinning wheel\", \"from\": 6574, \"to\": 6590}, {\"ngram\": \"a century\", \"from\": 6615, \"to\": 6624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story never satisfactorily told me whether she searched for the friends and family she had when she fell asleep or was happy enough with the prince who woke her up.Sleep is a pivotal part of these stories but also a dangerous twist in the tale.\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The story\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6635}, {\"ngram\": \"the friends\", \"from\": 6690, \"to\": 6701}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 6706, \"to\": 6712}, {\"ngram\": \"the prince\", \"from\": 6767, \"to\": 6777}, {\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6799}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal part\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6817}, {\"ngram\": \"these stories\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 6834}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerous twist\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6861}, {\"ngram\": \"the tale\", \"from\": 6865, \"to\": 6873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even shorter stints of sleep felt dangerous like Goldilocks who fell asleep after eating her porridge, only to wake up to three angry bears glaring at her.\", \"from\": 6875, \"to\": 7030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6924, \"end\": 6934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.114260820860471e-37, \"text\": \"Goldilocks\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even shorter stints\", \"from\": 6875, \"to\": 6894}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 6898, \"to\": 6903}, {\"ngram\": \"her porridge\", \"from\": 6964, \"to\": 6976}, {\"ngram\": \"to three angry bears\", \"from\": 6994, \"to\": 7014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snow White bit the poisoned apple and fell into a death-like slumber much to the sorrow of the seven dwarves who put her in a glass casket.\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7031, \"end\": 7041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3273218827307956e-64, \"text\": \"Snow White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the poisoned apple\", \"from\": 7046, \"to\": 7064}, {\"ngram\": \"the sorrow\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7118}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven dwarves\", \"from\": 7122, \"to\": 7139}, {\"ngram\": \"a glass casket\", \"from\": 7155, \"to\": 7169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That a handsome prince came and kissed the supposed corpse and brought her back to life only made the whole story more creepy.Sleep could be a perilous undertaking in those stories, a dangerous time when you let down your guard but sleeplessness was never the problem except for that one lonely princess who could not sleep because of the pea hidden under several mattresses.\", \"from\": 7171, \"to\": 7546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a handsome prince\", \"from\": 7176, \"to\": 7193}, {\"ngram\": \"the supposed corpse\", \"from\": 7210, \"to\": 7229}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 7254, \"to\": 7258}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole story\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7284}, {\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7302}, {\"ngram\": \"a perilous undertaking\", \"from\": 7312, \"to\": 7334}, {\"ngram\": \"those stories\", \"from\": 7338, \"to\": 7351}, {\"ngram\": \"your guard\", \"from\": 7388, \"to\": 7398}, {\"ngram\": \"sleeplessness\", \"from\": 7403, \"to\": 7416}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 7427, \"to\": 7438}, {\"ngram\": \"that one lonely princess\", \"from\": 7450, \"to\": 7474}, {\"ngram\": \"the pea\", \"from\": 7506, \"to\": 7513}, {\"ngram\": \"several mattresses\", \"from\": 7527, \"to\": 7545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that has become the fairytale of our lives.\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fairytale\", \"from\": 7567, \"to\": 7580}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in our version we do not win a prince at the end of it.\", \"from\": 7595, \"to\": 7654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our version\", \"from\": 7602, \"to\": 7613}, {\"ngram\": \"a prince\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7636}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 7640, \"to\": 7647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not even want one.\", \"from\": 7655, \"to\": 7679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a good night's sleep would be prize enough.Cult Friction is a fortnightly column on issues we keep rubbing up against.\", \"from\": 7680, \"to\": 7803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7733, \"end\": 7741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.725812036838855e-39, \"text\": \"Friction\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just a good night's sleep\", \"from\": 7680, \"to\": 7705}, {\"ngram\": \"a fortnightly column\", \"from\": 7745, \"to\": 7765}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 7769, \"to\": 7775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sandip Roy is a writer, journalist and radio host.\", \"from\": 7804, \"to\": 7854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sandip Roy\", \"from\": 7804, \"to\": 7814}, {\"ngram\": \"a writer\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7826}, {\"ngram\": \"journalist\", \"from\": 7828, \"to\": 7838}, {\"ngram\": \"radio host\", \"from\": 7843, \"to\": 7853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He posts @sandiprAlso read:How the Constitution played a pivotal role in the election But even those of us not chasing an Olympic medal know a thing or two about poor sleep.\", \"from\": 7855, \"to\": 8029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Constitution\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7902}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal role\", \"from\": 7910, \"to\": 7924}, {\"ngram\": \"the election\", \"from\": 7928, \"to\": 7940}, {\"ngram\": \"even those\", \"from\": 7945, \"to\": 7955}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7959, \"to\": 7961}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 7974, \"to\": 7990}, {\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 7996, \"to\": 8003}, {\"ngram\": \"poor sleep\", \"from\": 8017, \"to\": 8027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was the kind of boy who fell asleep as soon as his head hit the pillow.\", \"from\": 8030, \"to\": 8103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 8036, \"to\": 8044}, {\"ngram\": \"boy\", \"from\": 8048, \"to\": 8051}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 8079, \"to\": 8087}, {\"ngram\": \"the pillow\", \"from\": 8092, \"to\": 8102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I am the man who often wakes up with a jolt in the middle of night and frets and fumes listening to the city asleep around him.\", \"from\": 8104, \"to\": 8235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 8113, \"to\": 8120}, {\"ngram\": \"a jolt\", \"from\": 8145, \"to\": 8151}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 8155, \"to\": 8165}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 8169, \"to\": 8174}, {\"ngram\": \"frets\", \"from\": 8179, \"to\": 8184}, {\"ngram\": \"fumes\", \"from\": 8189, \"to\": 8194}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 8208, \"to\": 8216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night I go to bed wondering what kind of night it will be.\", \"from\": 8236, \"to\": 8300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 8256, \"to\": 8259}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 8270, \"to\": 8279}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 8283, \"to\": 8288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night of restful sleep feels like a minor victory.\", \"from\": 8301, \"to\": 8357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every night\", \"from\": 8301, \"to\": 8312}, {\"ngram\": \"restful sleep\", \"from\": 8316, \"to\": 8329}, {\"ngram\": \"a minor victory\", \"from\": 8341, \"to\": 8356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand it is part of growing older.\", \"from\": 8359, \"to\": 8400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 8378, \"to\": 8382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is something deeper going on.The Sleep Survey 2024conducted by ResMed, a medical device company, surveyed 17 countries.\", \"from\": 8401, \"to\": 8530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8414, \"to\": 8423}, {\"ngram\": \"The Sleep Survey\", \"from\": 8440, \"to\": 8456}, {\"ngram\": \"ResMed\", \"from\": 8474, \"to\": 8480}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical device company\", \"from\": 8482, \"to\": 8506}, {\"ngram\": \"17 countries\", \"from\": 8517, \"to\": 8529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It concluded that only 27% of Indians reported a good night's sleep each week.\", \"from\": 8531, \"to\": 8609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8561, \"end\": 8568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9973778045242311, \"rank\": 0.0016645993583474217, \"text\": \"Indians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 27%\", \"from\": 8549, \"to\": 8557}, {\"ngram\": \"a good night's sleep\", \"from\": 8578, \"to\": 8598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 2019 study by fitness band maker Fitbit concluded after analysing the data from Fitbit users that Indians were the second most sleep-deprived, among all the countries they surveyed, with Japan heading the list.\", \"from\": 8610, \"to\": 8822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8645, \"end\": 8651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fitbit\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\"}, {\"begin\": 8692, \"end\": 8698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fitbit\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fitbit\"}, {\"begin\": 8710, \"end\": 8717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9973778045242311, \"rank\": 0.0016645993583474217, \"text\": \"Indians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 8799, \"end\": 8804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9803891662861449, \"rank\": 0.019476335703717804, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A 2019 study\", \"from\": 8610, \"to\": 8622}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 8678, \"to\": 8686}, {\"ngram\": \"all the countries\", \"from\": 8761, \"to\": 8778}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 8813, \"to\": 8821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And their REM (rapid eye movement) sleep time was among the lowest in the world.\", \"from\": 8823, \"to\": 8903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(rapid eye movement\", \"from\": 8837, \"to\": 8856}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 8893, \"to\": 8902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know this only too well.\", \"from\": 8905, \"to\": 8931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Worried about my sleep, I got one of the fitness bands that would help monitor it.\", \"from\": 8932, \"to\": 9014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sleep\", \"from\": 8946, \"to\": 8954}, {\"ngram\": \"the fitness bands\", \"from\": 8969, \"to\": 8986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It ended up adding to my stress.\", \"from\": 9015, \"to\": 9047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my stress\", \"from\": 9037, \"to\": 9046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt like I was taking a sleeping test every night.\", \"from\": 9048, \"to\": 9102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sleeping test\", \"from\": 9074, \"to\": 9089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if I woke up refreshed and happy, it was never good enough for the nitpicking fitness band.\", \"from\": 9103, \"to\": 9199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nitpicking fitness band\", \"from\": 9171, \"to\": 9198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Try going to bed earlier,\\\" it would scold me.\", \"from\": 9200, \"to\": 9246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 9214, \"to\": 9217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My deep sleep time was invariably too low.\", \"from\": 9247, \"to\": 9289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My deep sleep time\", \"from\": 9247, \"to\": 9265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not strain yourself too much, keep good mood, make reasonable arrangements for work and rest time, and do more exercise to keep fit,\\\" it chirpily advised me.\", \"from\": 9290, \"to\": 9451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good mood\", \"from\": 9329, \"to\": 9338}, {\"ngram\": \"reasonable arrangements\", \"from\": 9345, \"to\": 9368}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 9373, \"to\": 9377}, {\"ngram\": \"rest time\", \"from\": 9382, \"to\": 9391}, {\"ngram\": \"more exercise\", \"from\": 9400, \"to\": 9413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to smack it.\", \"from\": 9452, \"to\": 9473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first time sleeplessness really hit me, I was recovering from jet lag.\", \"from\": 9475, \"to\": 9549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first time sleeplessness\", \"from\": 9475, \"to\": 9503}, {\"ngram\": \"jet lag\", \"from\": 9541, \"to\": 9548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every night, no matter what time I went to bed, I would bolt awake somewhere between 2 and 3 in the morning.\", \"from\": 9550, \"to\": 9658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what time\", \"from\": 9573, \"to\": 9582}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 9593, \"to\": 9596}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 9646, \"to\": 9657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At some point I thought some mechanism had just broken inside me and I would never get my sleep back.\", \"from\": 9659, \"to\": 9760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 9662, \"to\": 9672}, {\"ngram\": \"some mechanism\", \"from\": 9683, \"to\": 9697}, {\"ngram\": \"my sleep\", \"from\": 9746, \"to\": 9754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going to sleep without worrying about it felt like the ultimate luxury.\", \"from\": 9761, \"to\": 9832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ultimate luxury\", \"from\": 9812, \"to\": 9831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now my social media shows me endless ads for pillows, sleep yoga sessions, chewable melatonin tablets and herbal supplements.\", \"from\": 9834, \"to\": 9959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my social media\", \"from\": 9838, \"to\": 9853}, {\"ngram\": \"endless ads\", \"from\": 9863, \"to\": 9874}, {\"ngram\": \"pillows\", \"from\": 9879, \"to\": 9886}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep yoga sessions\", \"from\": 9888, \"to\": 9907}, {\"ngram\": \"chewable melatonin tablets\", \"from\": 9909, \"to\": 9935}, {\"ngram\": \"herbal supplements\", \"from\": 9940, \"to\": 9958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had no idea there was an entire cottage industry around getting to sleep and staying asleep.\", \"from\": 9960, \"to\": 10054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 9966, \"to\": 9973}, {\"ngram\": \"an entire cottage industry\", \"from\": 9984, \"to\": 10010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I started measuring my caffeine intake with a tooth comb, watched endless videos of the 4-7-8 breathing relaxation exercise, carefully rearranged my bed for optimal sleeping comfort and tried to give myself a cut-off time with digital devices.\", \"from\": 10055, \"to\": 10298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my caffeine intake\", \"from\": 10075, \"to\": 10093}, {\"ngram\": \"a tooth comb\", \"from\": 10099, \"to\": 10111}, {\"ngram\": \"endless videos\", \"from\": 10121, \"to\": 10135}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4-7-8 breathing relaxation exercise\", \"from\": 10139, \"to\": 10178}, {\"ngram\": \"my bed\", \"from\": 10201, \"to\": 10207}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal sleeping comfort\", \"from\": 10212, \"to\": 10236}, {\"ngram\": \"a cut-off time\", \"from\": 10262, \"to\": 10276}, {\"ngram\": \"digital devices\", \"from\": 10282, \"to\": 10297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But sleep proved to be an elusive creature, sneakingly evading all the traps and temptations I had laid out for it.\", \"from\": 10299, \"to\": 10414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 10303, \"to\": 10308}, {\"ngram\": \"an elusive creature\", \"from\": 10322, \"to\": 10341}, {\"ngram\": \"all the traps\", \"from\": 10362, \"to\": 10375}, {\"ngram\": \"temptations\", \"from\": 10380, \"to\": 10391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I was a child, no one really read me bedtime stores.\", \"from\": 10416, \"to\": 10473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 10427, \"to\": 10434}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 10436, \"to\": 10442}, {\"ngram\": \"bedtime stores\", \"from\": 10458, \"to\": 10472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My parents would turn off the main light and turn on a bedside lamp.\", \"from\": 10474, \"to\": 10542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My parents\", \"from\": 10474, \"to\": 10484}, {\"ngram\": \"the main light\", \"from\": 10500, \"to\": 10514}, {\"ngram\": \"a bedside lamp\", \"from\": 10527, \"to\": 10541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father would sit and read the paper by the light of the lamp, half-listening to my mother as she filled him in about the day in a low voice.\", \"from\": 10543, \"to\": 10686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My father\", \"from\": 10543, \"to\": 10552}, {\"ngram\": \"the paper\", \"from\": 10572, \"to\": 10581}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 10585, \"to\": 10594}, {\"ngram\": \"the lamp\", \"from\": 10598, \"to\": 10606}, {\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 10626, \"to\": 10635}, {\"ngram\": \"about the day\", \"from\": 10657, \"to\": 10670}, {\"ngram\": \"a low voice\", \"from\": 10674, \"to\": 10685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would lie in bed looking at the strange deformed shadows the bedside lamp cast on the ceiling.\", \"from\": 10687, \"to\": 10783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 10702, \"to\": 10705}, {\"ngram\": \"the strange deformed shadows\", \"from\": 10717, \"to\": 10745}, {\"ngram\": \"the bedside lamp\", \"from\": 10746, \"to\": 10762}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceiling\", \"from\": 10771, \"to\": 10782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My favourite sleep ritual was to pull the covers over me, hug my bolster pillow orpaash-baalish, and make up little stories in my head.\", \"from\": 10784, \"to\": 10919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My favourite sleep\", \"from\": 10784, \"to\": 10802}, {\"ngram\": \"the covers\", \"from\": 10822, \"to\": 10832}, {\"ngram\": \"little stories\", \"from\": 10893, \"to\": 10907}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 10911, \"to\": 10918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would imagine that under thatpaash-baalishwas a secret world where my toys and I could have a picnic.\", \"from\": 10920, \"to\": 11023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thatpaash\", \"from\": 10947, \"to\": 10956}, {\"ngram\": \"a secret world\", \"from\": 10968, \"to\": 10982}, {\"ngram\": \"my toys\", \"from\": 10989, \"to\": 10996}, {\"ngram\": \"a picnic\", \"from\": 11014, \"to\": 11022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was something Enid Blyton-ish about the whole affair but it worked like a charm.\", \"from\": 11024, \"to\": 11110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11044, \"end\": 11048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7176772293675345e-38, \"text\": \"Enid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 11034, \"to\": 11043}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole affair\", \"from\": 11066, \"to\": 11082}, {\"ngram\": \"a charm\", \"from\": 11102, \"to\": 11109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would be asleep long before I managed to come up with a full menu for the picnic.\", \"from\": 11111, \"to\": 11194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full menu\", \"from\": 11167, \"to\": 11178}, {\"ngram\": \"the picnic\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Years later someone told me that the biggest sleep-aid I had back then was not my imaginary picnics, but a sense of security about the real world around me.\", \"from\": 11195, \"to\": 11351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 11207, \"to\": 11214}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sleep-aid\", \"from\": 11228, \"to\": 11249}, {\"ngram\": \"my imaginary picnics\", \"from\": 11274, \"to\": 11294}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 11311, \"to\": 11319}, {\"ngram\": \"the real world\", \"from\": 11326, \"to\": 11340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was comfort in hearing the low voices of my parents, in knowing that I would wake up to them the next day.\", \"from\": 11352, \"to\": 11464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 11362, \"to\": 11369}, {\"ngram\": \"the low voices\", \"from\": 11381, \"to\": 11395}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 11399, \"to\": 11409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The murmur of their voices was the white noise lulling me to sleep.\", \"from\": 11465, \"to\": 11532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The murmur\", \"from\": 11465, \"to\": 11475}, {\"ngram\": \"their voices\", \"from\": 11479, \"to\": 11491}, {\"ngram\": \"the white noise\", \"from\": 11496, \"to\": 11511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As adults we struggle to find that security in a world which seems increasingly on edge.\", \"from\": 11534, \"to\": 11622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 11537, \"to\": 11543}, {\"ngram\": \"that security\", \"from\": 11564, \"to\": 11577}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 11581, \"to\": 11588}, {\"ngram\": \"edge\", \"from\": 11617, \"to\": 11621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Work, relationships and our own health all feel increasingly insecure.\", \"from\": 11623, \"to\": 11693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Work\", \"from\": 11623, \"to\": 11627}, {\"ngram\": \"relationships\", \"from\": 11629, \"to\": 11642}, {\"ngram\": \"our own health\", \"from\": 11647, \"to\": 11661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep is but a natural casualty.\", \"from\": 11694, \"to\": 11726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 11694, \"to\": 11699}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural casualty\", \"from\": 11707, \"to\": 11725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A ruffled mind is a ruffled pillow,\\\" the author Charlotte Bronte is reputed to have said.\", \"from\": 11727, \"to\": 11817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11776, \"end\": 11792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\", \"score\": 0.9999999619840317, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Bronte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Bront\\u00eb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A ruffled mind\", \"from\": 11728, \"to\": 11742}, {\"ngram\": \"a ruffled pillow\", \"from\": 11746, \"to\": 11762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We live in very ruffled times indeed.\", \"from\": 11818, \"to\": 11855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very ruffled times\", \"from\": 11829, \"to\": 11847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I would wake up with a start in the dead of night at first it would make me anxious.\", \"from\": 11857, \"to\": 11946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a start\", \"from\": 11883, \"to\": 11890}, {\"ngram\": \"the dead\", \"from\": 11894, \"to\": 11902}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 11906, \"to\": 11911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I try to make peace with it.\", \"from\": 11947, \"to\": 11979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 11965, \"to\": 11970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I stand on the balcony looking at the empty street in an entirely different light, the streetlights almost forlorn and ghostly.\", \"from\": 11980, \"to\": 12117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the empty street\", \"from\": 12024, \"to\": 12040}, {\"ngram\": \"an entirely different light\", \"from\": 12044, \"to\": 12071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recognise the street dogs out on patrol.\", \"from\": 12118, \"to\": 12160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 12130, \"to\": 12140}, {\"ngram\": \"patrol\", \"from\": 12153, \"to\": 12159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rats come out of holes and scurry around looking for food.\", \"from\": 12161, \"to\": 12223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rats\", \"from\": 12161, \"to\": 12169}, {\"ngram\": \"holes\", \"from\": 12182, \"to\": 12187}, {\"ngram\": \"scurry\", \"from\": 12192, \"to\": 12198}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 12218, \"to\": 12222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A sudden noise somewhere sets off a cawing frenzy among unseen crows.\", \"from\": 12224, \"to\": 12293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cawing frenzy\", \"from\": 12258, \"to\": 12273}, {\"ngram\": \"unseen crows\", \"from\": 12280, \"to\": 12292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I see the vegetable vendor doggedly pushing a cart of cabbages and tomatoes to set up for the next day.\", \"from\": 12294, \"to\": 12397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vegetable vendor\", \"from\": 12300, \"to\": 12320}, {\"ngram\": \"a cart\", \"from\": 12338, \"to\": 12344}, {\"ngram\": \"cabbages\", \"from\": 12348, \"to\": 12356}, {\"ngram\": \"tomatoes\", \"from\": 12361, \"to\": 12369}, {\"ngram\": \"the next day\", \"from\": 12384, \"to\": 12396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes a drunk staggers down the street jabbing at his phone probably trying to book an Uber.\", \"from\": 12398, \"to\": 12494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drunk staggers\", \"from\": 12408, \"to\": 12424}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 12430, \"to\": 12440}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 12452, \"to\": 12461}, {\"ngram\": \"an Uber\", \"from\": 12486, \"to\": 12493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young men who work at the cheap restaurant across the street wash dishes late into the night and finally relax, sprawled around the front steps, immersed in the flickering light of videos on their phones.\", \"from\": 12495, \"to\": 12703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The young men\", \"from\": 12495, \"to\": 12508}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheap restaurant\", \"from\": 12521, \"to\": 12541}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 12549, \"to\": 12559}, {\"ngram\": \"dishes\", \"from\": 12565, \"to\": 12571}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 12582, \"to\": 12591}, {\"ngram\": \"the front steps\", \"from\": 12627, \"to\": 12642}, {\"ngram\": \"the flickering light\", \"from\": 12656, \"to\": 12676}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 12680, \"to\": 12686}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 12690, \"to\": 12702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a rhythm here too, a soundscape that rustles to life once all the shops are shut and the buses and trams fall silent.\", \"from\": 12704, \"to\": 12830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rhythm\", \"from\": 12713, \"to\": 12721}, {\"ngram\": \"a soundscape\", \"from\": 12732, \"to\": 12744}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 12761, \"to\": 12765}, {\"ngram\": \"all the shops\", \"from\": 12771, \"to\": 12784}, {\"ngram\": \"the buses\", \"from\": 12798, \"to\": 12807}, {\"ngram\": \"trams\", \"from\": 12812, \"to\": 12817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I think back to childhood stories, the problem seems to have always been too much sleep as opposed to too little.\", \"from\": 12832, \"to\": 12950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"childhood stories\", \"from\": 12853, \"to\": 12870}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 12872, \"to\": 12883}, {\"ngram\": \"too much sleep\", \"from\": 12910, \"to\": 12924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kumbhakarna, Rip van Winkle and Sleeping Beauty all had sleep disorders but none of them were afflicted by insomnia.\", \"from\": 12951, \"to\": 13067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12951, \"end\": 12962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\", \"score\": 0.9999999998181011, \"rank\": 1.8200280897676406e-10, \"text\": \"Kumbhakarna\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kumbhakarna\"}, {\"begin\": 12964, \"end\": 12978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4143465589471975e-57, \"text\": \"Rip van Winkle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleeping Beauty\", \"from\": 12983, \"to\": 12998}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep disorders\", \"from\": 13007, \"to\": 13022}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 13027, \"to\": 13031}, {\"ngram\": \"insomnia\", \"from\": 13058, \"to\": 13066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the Bengali fairytales I read had princesses who kept falling asleep and needed some prince with a golden wand to wake them.\", \"from\": 13068, \"to\": 13197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13077, \"end\": 13084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\", \"score\": 0.9999605449064164, \"rank\": 3.945664875035729e-05, \"text\": \"Bengali\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bengali_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"princesses\", \"from\": 13107, \"to\": 13117}, {\"ngram\": \"some prince\", \"from\": 13153, \"to\": 13164}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden wand\", \"from\": 13170, \"to\": 13183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Too much sleep was scary in those fairytales.\", \"from\": 13198, \"to\": 13243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Too much sleep\", \"from\": 13198, \"to\": 13212}, {\"ngram\": \"those fairytales\", \"from\": 13226, \"to\": 13242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rip van Winkle woke up after 20 years to find that his wife was long dead and the American revolution had happened.\", \"from\": 13244, \"to\": 13359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13244, \"end\": 13258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4143465589471975e-57, \"text\": \"Rip van Winkle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rip_Van_Winkle\"}, {\"begin\": 13326, \"end\": 13345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\", \"score\": 0.9999290548022813, \"rank\": 7.095023122573333e-05, \"text\": \"American revolution\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Revolution\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 13273, \"to\": 13281}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 13295, \"to\": 13303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleeping Beauty pricked her finger on a spinning wheel and did not wake up for a century.\", \"from\": 13360, \"to\": 13449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleeping Beauty\", \"from\": 13360, \"to\": 13375}, {\"ngram\": \"her finger\", \"from\": 13384, \"to\": 13394}, {\"ngram\": \"a spinning wheel\", \"from\": 13398, \"to\": 13414}, {\"ngram\": \"a century\", \"from\": 13439, \"to\": 13448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story never satisfactorily told me whether she searched for the friends and family she had when she fell asleep or was happy enough with the prince who woke her up.\", \"from\": 13450, \"to\": 13618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The story\", \"from\": 13450, \"to\": 13459}, {\"ngram\": \"the friends\", \"from\": 13514, \"to\": 13525}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 13530, \"to\": 13536}, {\"ngram\": \"the prince\", \"from\": 13591, \"to\": 13601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep is a pivotal part of these stories but also a dangerous twist in the tale.\", \"from\": 13620, \"to\": 13700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 13620, \"to\": 13625}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal part\", \"from\": 13629, \"to\": 13643}, {\"ngram\": \"these stories\", \"from\": 13647, \"to\": 13660}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerous twist\", \"from\": 13670, \"to\": 13687}, {\"ngram\": \"the tale\", \"from\": 13691, \"to\": 13699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even shorter stints of sleep felt dangerous like Goldilocks who fell asleep after eating her porridge, only to wake up to three angry bears glaring at her.\", \"from\": 13701, \"to\": 13856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13750, \"end\": 13760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.114260820860471e-37, \"text\": \"Goldilocks\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldilocks_and_the_Three_Bears\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even shorter stints\", \"from\": 13701, \"to\": 13720}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 13724, \"to\": 13729}, {\"ngram\": \"her porridge\", \"from\": 13790, \"to\": 13802}, {\"ngram\": \"to three angry bears\", \"from\": 13820, \"to\": 13840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snow White bit the poisoned apple and fell into a death-like slumber much to the sorrow of the seven dwarves who put her in a glass casket.\", \"from\": 13857, \"to\": 13996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13857, \"end\": 13867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3273218827307956e-64, \"text\": \"Snow White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snow_White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the poisoned apple\", \"from\": 13872, \"to\": 13890}, {\"ngram\": \"the sorrow\", \"from\": 13934, \"to\": 13944}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven dwarves\", \"from\": 13948, \"to\": 13965}, {\"ngram\": \"a glass casket\", \"from\": 13981, \"to\": 13995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That a handsome prince came and kissed the supposed corpse and brought her back to life only made the whole story more creepy.\", \"from\": 13997, \"to\": 14123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a handsome prince\", \"from\": 14002, \"to\": 14019}, {\"ngram\": \"the supposed corpse\", \"from\": 14036, \"to\": 14055}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 14080, \"to\": 14084}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole story\", \"from\": 14095, \"to\": 14110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep could be a perilous undertaking in those stories, a dangerous time when you let down your guard but sleeplessness was never the problem except for that one lonely princess who could not sleep because of the pea hidden under several mattresses.\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sleep\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14130}, {\"ngram\": \"a perilous undertaking\", \"from\": 14140, \"to\": 14162}, {\"ngram\": \"those stories\", \"from\": 14166, \"to\": 14179}, {\"ngram\": \"your guard\", \"from\": 14216, \"to\": 14226}, {\"ngram\": \"sleeplessness\", \"from\": 14231, \"to\": 14244}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 14255, \"to\": 14266}, {\"ngram\": \"that one lonely princess\", \"from\": 14278, \"to\": 14302}, {\"ngram\": \"the pea\", \"from\": 14334, \"to\": 14341}, {\"ngram\": \"several mattresses\", \"from\": 14355, \"to\": 14373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that has become the fairytale of our lives.\", \"from\": 14375, \"to\": 14422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fairytale\", \"from\": 14395, \"to\": 14408}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 14412, \"to\": 14421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in our version we do not win a prince at the end of it.\", \"from\": 14423, \"to\": 14482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our version\", \"from\": 14430, \"to\": 14441}, {\"ngram\": \"a prince\", \"from\": 14456, \"to\": 14464}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 14468, \"to\": 14475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not even want one.\", \"from\": 14483, \"to\": 14507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a good night's sleep would be prize enough.\", \"from\": 14508, \"to\": 14556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just a good night's sleep\", \"from\": 14508, \"to\": 14533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cult Friction is a fortnightly column on issues we keep rubbing up against.\", \"from\": 14558, \"to\": 14633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14563, \"end\": 14571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.725812036838855e-39, \"text\": \"Friction\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friction\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fortnightly column\", \"f